DefaultDescription: An AutoDriller stores items in a similar way to a chest, but allows dispensing them through the hole and drill the block when triggered via rising edge of an electric signal. It can either dispense the item or keep it, depending on the setting.
An AutoCrusher can crush the material ore or rock in a second, a very convenient and wide-range-usded machine in early industrial era.
The symbol of the early industrial era, an great invention that can liberate human labor force.
A Diversion can veer a projectile when hitting it.

An Ironfurnace is an enclosure made from fire resistant stone and iron, in which a high temperature is maintained by burning combustible fuel. It is an important item that allows smelting, cooking and other forms of heat processing. The best fuel for the furnace are coal chunks, but wood and even leaves can be used if coal is unavailable. IronFurnace can be left unattended while working. It also emits a small amount of light.
A machine that can press the metal to get metal plate.
Coalpowder is black powder obtained by crushing coal chunk. It can be used to be fuel.
A machine that can smash the chunk to get powder.
The basic case of some machine. Very heavy and durable. Extremely resilient to digging and explosions. Can be crafted from multiple ironplate or steel ingots.
A machine that can rifle the steelrod or alloyrod to get rifle barrel.
A Rifle can be used to fire metal bullet. You can shot two times because the rifle can contain two bullet, an powerful weapon during the initial industrial era.
Bullets are fired from firearms.

Shovels are tools for digging blocks made of loose material, such as sand or gravel. They greatly speed up the digging process, but eventually they will get damaged and fail. Shovels made of better materials last longer and dig faster.

Pickaxes are tools for quarrying hard blocks, such as stone or ice. They greatly speed up the quarrying process, but eventually they will get damaged and fail. Pickaxes made of better materials last longer and quarry faster.

Axes are tools for cutting soft blocks, such as wood, furniture or leaves. They greatly speed up the cutting process, but eventually they will get damaged and fail. Axes made of better materials last longer and cut faster. Axe is also a powerful weapon, although it is very difficult to hit a moving target.

Rakes are tools for turning dirt into soil. After the soil has been created by a rake, it is ready to be planted. The rake will eventually get damaged and fail. Rakes made of better materials last longer.

A spear is a versatile weapon that can be both thrown and used for melee attacks. When used, it will eventually lose its sharpness and fail. Spears made with better materials will last longer and cause more damage. Thrown spears will stick in soft materials. It may be hard to remove a spear which embedded itself too hard.

A machete is a simple sword like slashing weapon that is very effective for melee attacks. When used, the machete will gradually lose its sharpness and eventually fail. Machetes made of better materials will last longer and cause more damage.
The Container of some chemical material. Very heavy and durable. Very important in the chemical field.
A Strling engine is a kind of heat engine that operates by cyclic compression and expansion of air or other gas at different temperature in a closed thermodynamic system.
Drill is the most important part in the autodriller, you should put it in the machine while using it. Reminding, mining will damage the drill.
A Liquidpump stores items in a similar way to a chest, but allows dispensing them through the hole and pump the liquid under it when triggered via rising edge of an electric signal.
The device is used to provide blast of hot air to the blast furnace, so that the chemical recation can take place throughout the furnace.
An Blast furnace is a type of metallurgical furnace used for smelting to produce industrial metals generally iron, but also others like lead or copper.
A Furnace in which fuel is burned.

Casting Machine provides a manufacturing process in which a liquid material is usually poured into a mold, which contains a hollow cavity of thr desired shape, and then allowed to solidify.It is often used for making complex shapes that would be otherwise difficult or uneconomical to make by other methods.
A machine that can squeeze the metal ingot to get metal line.
Ivy is a plant that grows and clings to vertical surfaces. It does not require much light to stay alive, but needs a humid and warm climate.

machine tool is a piece of workshop furniture made of metal. It is a very important item in the industrial era, because it allows you to craft items that require more than 3x3 crafting slots. A lots of craftable industiral items or machine can be made on it, provided that you have the required materials.
